Workflow.Name: Power automate desktop
Workflow.Definition:
"@@ConnectionString: ''
@@Type: 'Local'
@@DesktopType: 'local'
@@DisplayName: 'Local computer'
IMPORT 'controlRepo.appmask' AS appmask
IMPORT 'imageRepo.imgrepo' AS imgrepo
@SENSITIVE: []
WebAutomation.LaunchChrome.LaunchChrome Url: $'''https://www.powerautomatetutorials.com/power-automate-desktop-beginners-course/chapter-4-variables/''' WindowState: WebAutomation.BrowserWindowState.Normal ClearCache: False ClearCookies: False WaitForPageToLoadTimeout: 60 Timeout: 60 BrowserInstance=> Browser
WebAutomation.GetDetailsOfElement BrowserInstance: Browser Control: appmask['Web Page \'h ... variables/\'']['Span \'15KG\''] AttributeName: $'''Own Text''' AttributeValue=> suitcase1
WebAutomation.GetDetailsOfElement BrowserInstance: Browser Control: appmask['Web Page \'h ... variables/\'']['Span \'20KG\''] AttributeName: $'''Own Text''' AttributeValue=> suitcase2
WebAutomation.GetDetailsOfElement BrowserInstance: Browser Control: appmask['Web Page \'h ... variables/\'']['Span \'40KG\''] AttributeName: $'''Own Text''' AttributeValue=> MaxWeight
Text.CropText.CropTextBeforeFlag Text: suitcase1 ToFlag: $'''KG''' IgnoreCase: False CroppedText=> suitcase1_cropped IsFlagFound=> IsFlagFound
Text.CropText.CropTextBeforeFlag Text: suitcase2 ToFlag: $'''KG''' IgnoreCase: False CroppedText=> suitcase2_cropped IsFlagFound=> IsFlagFound2
Text.CropText.CropTextBeforeFlag Text: MaxWeight ToFlag: $'''KG''' IgnoreCase: False CroppedText=> Max_weight_cropped IsFlagFound=> IsFlagFound3
Text.ToNumber Text: suitcase1_cropped Number=> suitcase1_number
Text.ToNumber Text: suitcase2_cropped Number=> suitcase2_number
Text.ToNumber Text: Max_weight_cropped Number=> Max_weight_number
SET total_suitcase_weight TO $'''%suitcase1_number% + %suitcase2_number% '''
IF total_suitcase_weight = Max_weight_number THEN
 Display.ShowMessageDialog.ShowMessage Message: $'''you\'re good, you did\'nt exceed max bagage''' Icon: Display.Icon.None Buttons: Display.Buttons.OK DefaultButton: Display.DefaultButton.Button1 IsTopMost: False ButtonPressed=> ButtonPressed
ELSE
 Display.ShowMessageDialog.ShowMessage Message: $'''STOP! Too much bagage''' Icon: Display.Icon.None Buttons: Display.Buttons.OK DefaultButton: Display.DefaultButton.Button1 IsTopMost: False ButtonPressed=> ButtonPressed2
END
"

Workflow.Name: Web Data Scraping and Reporting
Workflow.Definition:
"@@ConnectionString: ''
@@Type: 'Local'
@@DesktopType: 'local'
@@DisplayName: 'Local computer'
IMPORT 'controlRepo.appmask' AS appmask
IMPORT 'imageRepo.imgrepo' AS imgrepo
@SENSITIVE: []
WebAutomation.LaunchChrome.LaunchChrome Url: $'''https://www.xelplus.com/all-tutorials/''' WindowState: WebAutomation.BrowserWindowState.Normal ClearCache: False ClearCookies: False WaitForPageToLoadTimeout: 60 Timeout: 60 BrowserInstance=> Browser
# Start of autogenerated actions using the recorder
WebAutomation.ExtractData.ExtractTable BrowserInstance: Browser Control: $'''html > body > div:eq(4) > main > div > div > div > div > div:eq(1) > div > turbo-frame > div > div:eq(0) > div''' ExtractionParameters: {[$'''div:eq(1) > h2 > a''', $'''Own Text''', $'''''', $'''Value #1'''], [$'''div:eq(1) > h2 > a''', $'''Href''', $'''''', $'''Value #2'''] } PostProcessData: False TimeoutInSeconds: 60 ExtractedData=> ExtractedData
# End of autogenerated actions using the recorder
Excel.LaunchExcel.LaunchAndOpenUnderExistingProcess Path: $'''C:\\Users\\Amar\\Desktop\\Web Data Scraping.xlsx''' Visible: True ReadOnly: False Instance=> ExcelInstance
Excel.WriteToExcel.WriteCell Instance: ExcelInstance Value: ExtractedData Column: 2 Row: 1
Excel.SaveExcel.SaveAs Instance: ExcelInstance DocumentFormat: Excel.ExcelFormat.OpenXmlWorkbook DocumentPath: $'''C:\\Users\\Amar\\Desktop\\Web data'''
Excel.CloseExcel.CloseAndSave Instance: ExcelInstance
"
